from Apocalypse. His eyes glowed. "Lets kill it." He looked at his followers. 
"God neptune will accompany us guiledart will stay here." He pulled off the 
disc from guiledart. He put it on Darkmouse's shoulder. "This will block your 
signal from, beng detected...helps the eliminate of surprise." The door slid 
open.."Ladies first."
